channel.description:
This is a catchup on television channel for stuff you missed when it aired live and you would like to relive the memories again from big events that air on TV. It is specifically targeted towards international viewers who want to catch American/Canadian television that they don't have access to in their countries.

If you enjoy the content on this channel and want to support the hard work displayed on the editing of these videos then please donate via Patreon on this page here: https://www.patreon.com/SamsSecretClassicCollection?ty=h
channel.title: Samantha's Secret Classic Collection
